	* Makefile.PL, t/00Shell-GetEnv.t, t/envstr.t, t/exclude.t,
	t/import_envs.t, t/redirect.t:
	kill tests if they hang for more than 10 seconds; save test STDERR &
	STDOUT

	In order to ensure that tests don't hang because of bizarrities in
	the user's shell profiles, cause tests to timeout after 10 seconds.
	The shell output is now saved (previously it was discarded).

